(29, 'Beach Vacations', 'lotus-temple-16771585311462.jpeg', 'lotus temple', 'beach-vacations', '<p>test data</p>', 'test data', 'test data', '2023-02-23 13:22:13', '2023-02-23 13:22:13'),
(30, 'Beach holidays:', 'beach-1677176503774012.webp', 'beach', 'beach-holidays', '<p>India has a <strong>vast coastline</strong>, with some of the world\'s most beautiful beaches. The coastal states of Goa, Kerala, Andaman, and Lakshadweep are known for their white sandy beaches, crystal-clear waters, and stunning sunsets. The beaches of Goa are known for their vibrant nightlife, while the beaches of Kerala are known for their calm and serene atmosphere. Andaman and Lakshadweep offer a unique experience of beaches with pristine coral reefs and marine life. These destinations are perfect for those looking for a relaxing beach holiday, with options for water sports, beach parties, and seafood delicacies.</p>', '\"Discover India\'s Best Beaches for Your Next Vacation\", \"Unwind in Paradise: Beach Holidays in India\", \"From Serenity to Adventure: Beach Holidays for All in India\", \"Escape to the Sun and Sand: Beach Holidays Across India\", \"Beach Bumming in India: Top D', 'beach holidays, India beach vacations, beach destinations in India, coastal holidays, beach getaways, Indian beaches, beach resorts in India, beach vacation packages, beach travel in India, best beaches in India', '2023-02-23 18:21:44', '2023-02-24 09:23:44'),
(31, 'Hill station holidays', 'hill-station-167717670136268.webp', 'hill station', 'hill-station-holidays', '<p>India has a plethora of picturesque hill stations, perfect for a summer getaway. From the northern states of Himachal Pradesh, Uttarakhand, and Jammu and Kashmir to the southern state of Tamil Nadu, the country is dotted with charming hill stations. These destinations offer scenic views, pleasant weather, and a chance to escape the heat of the plains. Whether it\'s trekking, camping, or just a leisurely stroll amidst the lush greenery, hill stations in India have something for everyone.</p>', 'Discover the Beauty of Indian Hill Stations, Enjoy a Memorable Hill Station Holiday in India - Top Destinations, Best Hill Station Holidays', 'hill station holidays, hill stations in India, scenic mountain getaways, nature retreats, summer vacations, winter escapes, family holidays, adventure trips, honeymoon destinations, picturesque landscapes.', '2023-02-23 18:25:02', '2023-02-24 09:23:06'),
(32, 'Desert holidays', 'desert-1677176981985003.jpeg', 'desert', 'desert-holidays', '<p>Experience the magic of the <strong>Thar Desert</strong> with our desert holidays. From the vast stretches of sand dunes to the majestic forts and palaces, the desert state of Rajasthan offers a truly unique and unforgettable experience. Take a camel ride through the golden sands, watch the sunset over the dunes, and immerse yourself in the vibrant local culture. Whether you want to explore the historic cities of Jaipur, Jodhpur, and Udaipur or stay in a luxurious desert camp, our desert holidays have something for everyone. Get ready for an adventure of a lifetime in the heart of India\'s desert region.</p>', 'Desert Holidays in Rajasthan , Explore the Magic of Thar Desert , Discover the Enchanting Desert of India: Desert Holidays', 'Desert Holidays, Desert Adventures, Rajasthan Tour, Jaisalmer, Camel Safari, Desert Culture, Desert FestivalsRajasthan, sand dunes, camel ride, Jaipur, Jodhpur, Udaipur, luxury desert camp', '2023-02-23 18:29:41', '2023-02-24 05:46:14'),
(33, 'Wildlife holidays', 'wildlife-sanctuaries-1677239374364827.jpeg', '-wildlife-sanctuaries', 'wildlife-holidays', '<p>India is home to a wide variety of wildlife, including <strong>tigers, lions, elephants, and rhinos</strong>. The country has several national parks and wildlife sanctuaries, including the famous<strong> Jim Corbett National Park, Ranthambore National Park, and Bandhavgarh National Park</strong>. These destinations offer a chance to witness these majestic animals in their natural habitat, along with opportunities for bird watching and nature walks.</p>', 'Wildlife Holidays in India - Explore the Wild Side of India, \"Unleash Your Wild Side: The Best Wildlife Holidays in India\", \"Tiger Spotting in India: A Wildlife Lover\'s Dream\", \"Jungle Safaris in India: Get Up Close and Personal with Wildlife\", \"Bird Watc', 'Wildlife Safaris, Jungle Adventure, Wildlife Sanctuaries, National Parks, India Wildlife Tours', '2023-02-24 11:49:35', '2023-02-24 11:50:07'),
(34, 'Backwater holidays', 'backwaters-1677239568120840.jpeg', 'backwaters', 'backwater-holidays', '<p>Explore the tranquil beauty of Kerala\'s backwaters with our backwater holidays. From cruising down the<strong> palm-fringed canals to relaxing in a luxurious houseboat, </strong>the backwaters of Kerala offer a truly unique and rejuvenating experience. Experience the<strong> lush greenery, the tranquil waters, and the vibrant local culture of the region</strong>. Whether you want to stay in a traditional Kerala homestay or a luxurious resort, our backwater holidays have something for everyone. Get ready to unwind and rejuvenate your mind, body, and soul in the lap of nature.</p>', 'Backwater Holidays in Kerala, Explore the Tranquil Beauty of the Backwater', 'backwater holidays, Kerala, houseboat, palm-fringed canals, local culture, homestay, luxurious resort', '2023-02-24 11:52:50', '2023-02-24 11:52:50'),
(35, 'Cultural Holidays', 'golden-temple-1677262273216555.webp', 'Golden-Temple', 'cultural-holidays', '<p>India is known for its rich cultural heritage, with diverse traditions and customs across its different states. From the Mughal architecture of Delhi to the Dravidian temples of Tamil Nadu, there\'s no shortage of cultural attractions in India. Rajasthan is known for its royal forts and palaces, while the state of Gujarat is famous for its colorful festivals and handicrafts. These destinations are perfect for those interested in exploring India\'s history, art, and traditions.</p>', '\"Embark on a Cultural Journey to India: Vacation Packages for Rajasthan\", \"Experience the Diversity of India: Packages for Cultural Vacations in Kerala\", \"Explore the Rich Cultural Heritage of Tamil Nadu: Vacation Packages Available\", \"Discover the Mystic', 'Cultural beach vacation packages India, Cultural Holidays, Indian Heritage, Historical Sites, Cultural Tours, Traditional Festivals', '2023-02-24 18:11:15', '2023-02-24 18:11:15'),
(36, 'Adventure holidays', 'adventure-1677344554942502.jpeg', 'adventure', 'adventure-holidays', '<p>India has a diverse landscape, ranging from the snow-capped Himalayas to the sandy deserts of Rajasthan. This makes it an ideal destination for adventure sports enthusiasts. From trekking in the Himalayas to rafting in the Ganges, from skiing in Gulmarg to paragliding in Kamshet, there\'s no dearth of adventure activities in India. These destinations are perfect for those seeking an adrenaline rush and a sense of adventure.</p>', 'Experience Thrills and Adventure with Our Adventure Holidays in India', 'Adventure Holidays, Trekking, Wildlife Safari, Water Sports, Camping, Biking', '2023-02-25 17:02:35', '2023-02-25 17:02:35'),
(37, 'Spiritual holidays', 'spiritual-tour-of-india-this-holiday-season-1-1677344667536666.jpeg', 'spiritual-tour-of-india-this-holiday-season-1', 'spiritual-holidays', '<p>Discover the spiritual side of India with our spiritual holidays. India is home to some of the world\'s most sacred and holy sites, from the Ganges River to the temples of South India. Immerse yourself in the ancient wisdom of yoga and meditation, explore the vibrant local culture, and connect with your inner self. Whether you want to embark on a pilgrimage to the holy cities of Varanasi and Rishikesh or experience the rich spiritual heritage of South India, our spiritual holidays have something for everyone. Get ready to awaken your senses and discover a deeper connection with the world around you.</p>', 'Spiritual Holidays in India, Embark on a Journey of Inner Awakening', 'spiritual holidays, yoga, meditation, holy sites, pilgrimage, Varanasi, Rishikesh, South India', '2023-02-25 17:04:28', '2023-02-25 17:04:28'),
(38, 'Luxury and Wellness holidays', 'luxury-wellness-1677344781103436.jpeg', 'luxury wellness', 'luxury-and-wellness-holidays', '<p>Indulge in the ultimate luxury and wellness experience with our luxury and wellness holidays. Whether you want to relax in a luxurious spa, rejuvenate with Ayurvedic treatments, or stay in a five-star resort, we have the perfect package for you. Explore the rich cultural heritage of India, savor the flavors of local cuisine, and pamper yourself with luxurious amenities. Whether you want to visit the majestic Taj Mahal, explore the vibrant cities of Delhi and Mumbai or relax on a pristine beach in Goa, our luxury and wellness holidays have something for everyone. Get ready to indulge in a world of luxury and rejuvenation.</p>', 'Luxury and Wellness Holidays in India, Indulge in Ultimate Pampering', 'luxury and wellness holidays, Ayurvedic treatments, five-star resorts, cultural heritage, local cuisine, Taj Mahal, Delhi, Mumbai, Goa.', '2023-02-25 17:06:22', '2023-02-25 17:06:22');
