(227, 3, '3', 'Sawai Madhopur', 'Sawai Madhopur', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Early morning leave for <strong>Jeep Safari</strong> in <strong>Ranthambore National Park</strong> to spot wild animals like tiger, wild boar, cheetal, barking deer and various species of birds. Return to the hotel for breakfast. &nbsp;Post lunch visit <strong>Ranthambore Fort</strong>. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Ranthambore</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 07:54:53', '2023-02-27 07:54:53'),
