(239, 4, '3', 'Amritsar', 'Dharamsala', '<p>After breakfast leave <strong>Amritsar</strong> for <strong>Dharamshala</strong>.&nbsp;Arrive <strong>Dharamshala</strong>, transfer to the hotel. After lunch visit <strong>Dalai Lamas Spiritual Center</strong>, <strong>Bakshunath Temple</strong> (to view the scenic beauty of the Himalian Hills).&nbsp;Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Dharamshala</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:02:56', '2023-02-27 08:02:56'),
