(244, 2, '1', 'Vijayawada', 'Hyderabad', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Leave <strong>Vijayawada</strong> for <strong>Hyderabad</strong> by bus at <strong>22:00 Hrs. (10:00 PM)</strong>. Overnight journey by the A/c bus.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(245, 2, '2', 'Hyderabad', 'New Delhi', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Arrive Hyderabad and transfer to <strong>Rajiv Gandhi International Airport</strong> to board flight for <strong>Delhi . </strong>Arrive <strong>Delhi</strong> at <strong>07:25(AM) Hrs. </strong>After wash n change and breakfast, visit <strong>Qutub Minar, India Gate with Kartvya Path</strong>, <strong>Parliament House </strong>, <strong>Rashtrapati Bhawan (from outside).</strong>Lunch at <strong>Akshardham temple. </strong>Enjoy the <strong>Pradarshini(exhibition)</strong> with <strong>evening laser show</strong> and learn about the life of Swami Narayan Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Delhi</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(246, 2, '3', 'New Delhi', 'Shimla', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">After Breakfast, visit <strong>Museum Of Illusion </strong>to learn about the concepts and implementation of Physics, followed by lunch. Post lunch visit <strong>the Prime Minister Sangrahalaya </strong>to learn about the events and decisions, our leaders of the country have taken for the betterment of India. After early dinner, leave <strong>Delhi </strong>for <strong>Shimla. </strong>Overnight journey by the A/c bus.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(247, 2, '4', 'Shimla', 'Shimla', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Breakfast to be served on the way. Arrive <strong>Chail (Shimla) </strong>and check in to the hotel in Chail (Shimla). After wash and change meet and greet the camp coordinator. The Camp-coordinator will guide you through the various activities which includes, Burma Bridge, Commando Net and Tarzan Rope. Post lunch return to the rest of the adventure activities. Enjoy the sizzling evening snacks and Bonfire. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Chail (Shimla)</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(248, 2, '5', 'Shimla', 'Manali', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Rise up early for morning trek in the midst of <strong>Pine Tree Forest</strong>. Return to the Hotel/camp for breakfast. After breakfast, visit <strong>Kufri </strong>to view the snow-covered peaks. Lunch at Shimla. Post lunch, visit the famous <strong>Sankat Hanuman Temple </strong>and <strong>Institute of Advance Studies. </strong>In the evening stroll to <strong>Mall Road </strong>and <strong>Lakkar Bazar</strong>. After early dinner<strong> </strong>leave <strong>Shimla</strong> for <strong>Manali. </strong>Overnight journey in the A/c bus</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(249, 2, '6', 'Manali', 'Manali', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Arrive <strong>Manali. </strong>After wash n change and breakfast, visit <strong>Hidimba Devi Temple </strong>(It is an ancient cave temple dedicated to Hidimba Devi, wife of Bhima, a figure in the Indian epic Mahabharata. The temple is surrounded by a cedar forest called Dhungiri Van Vihar at the foot of the Himalayas),<strong>Tibetans Monastery</strong>. Post lunch enjoy your visit to <strong>Club house</strong>. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Manali</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(250, 2, '7', 'Manali', 'Manali', '<p>After breakfast, leave for <strong>Solang Valley/gulaba </strong>to enjoy the scenic view of snow- covered peaks and play with snow. Return to the hotel. Enroute visit <strong>Vashist Sulphur Spring</strong>, <strong>Jogini Waterfall</strong>. Post lunch trek to the <strong>Mall Road</strong>. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Manali</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(251, 2, '8', 'Manali', 'Chandigarh', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">After early breakfast, leave <strong>Manali </strong>for <strong>Chandigarh</strong>. Arrive <strong>Chandigarh</strong> in the evening at <strong>17:00 Hrs (05:00 PM)</strong>. Visit <strong>Rock Garden</strong>, <strong>Sukhna Lake</strong>. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Chandigarh</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(252, 2, '9', 'Chandigarh', 'New Delhi', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">After breakfast, leave <strong>Chandigarh</strong> for <strong>Delhi</strong>. Arrive <strong>Delhi</strong>. Day free for shopping. In the evening leave by air for <strong>Hyderabad </strong>Arrive <strong>Hyderabad</strong>. Transfer to the A/c coach and leave for <strong>Vijaywada</strong>. Overnight journey by the bus</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(253, 2, '10', 'Vijayawada', 'Vijayawada', '<p>Arrive <strong>Vijayawada</strong> by early morning.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:33:35', '2023-02-27 08:33:35'),
(254, 12, '1', 'Hyderabad', 'New Delhi', '<p>Leave Hyderabad<strong> </strong>by <strong>Telangana Express (12723)</strong> for <strong>Delhi</strong> at <strong>06:00(AM) Hrs. </strong>Lunch in the train.<strong> </strong>Dinner and overnight journey in the train.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(255, 12, '2', 'New Delhi', 'Shimla', '<p>Arrive <strong>Delhi</strong> at <strong>07:40 Hrs.</strong> Transfer to hotel for wash and change. After breakfast visit, <strong>Lotus Temple</strong> followed by visiting <strong>Akshardham Temple.</strong> Lunch at Akshardham Temple. Post lunch, visit<strong> India Gate, Parliament House, Rastrapati Bhawan, Kartavya Path (from outside).</strong> After early dinner leave <strong>Delhi</strong> by bus for <strong>Shimla</strong>. Overnight journey in the bus.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(256, 12, '3', 'Shimla', 'Shimla', '<p>Arrive <strong>Shimla</strong> and transfer to the hotel. After breakfast visit <strong>Kufri. </strong>Post lunch, visit <strong>Lakkar Bazar</strong>, <strong>The Mall</strong>.<span style=\"color: red;\"> </span>Evening free for independent activities and shopping. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Shimla</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(257, 12, '4', 'Shimla', 'Manali', '<p>After breakfast, leave <strong>Shimla</strong> for <strong>Manali</strong>, lunch on the way. Arrive <strong>Manali</strong> and transfer to the hotel. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Manali</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(258, 12, '5', 'Manali', 'Manali', '<p>After breakfast, leave by Jeeps/ Jongas to visit <strong>Solang Pass</strong>. On return visit <strong>Vashist Sulpher Spring</strong>. Evening free for shopping. Dinner with dance party at hotel. Overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Manali</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(259, 12, '6', 'Manali', 'New Delhi', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">After breakfast track to <strong>Hadimba Devi Temple</strong>, <strong>Tibetan Monastery</strong>. Post lunch, leave <strong>Manali</strong> for <strong>Delhi</strong>. Dinner and overnight journey in the bus.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(260, 12, '7', 'New Delhi', 'Hyderabad', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Arrive <strong>Delhi</strong> and transfer to hotel for wash &amp; change. After breakfast, visit <strong>Qutub Minar</strong> (The Qutb Minar, also spelled Qutub Minar and Qutab Minar, is a minaret and \"victory tower\" that forms part of the Qutb complex, which lies at the site of Delhis oldest fortified city) and <strong>Airforce Museum</strong>. Post lunch, transfer to the <strong>New Delhi Railway Station to board Telangana Express (12724) </strong>for <strong>Hyderabad</strong> at <strong>17:25 hrs</strong>. Overnight Journey in the train.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(261, 12, '8', 'Hyderabad', 'Hyderabad', '<p>Arrive <strong>Hyderabad</strong> at <strong>19:50 hrs. (07:50 PM).</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:39:53', '2023-02-27 08:39:53'),
(262, 10, '1', 'Hyderabad', 'New Delhi', '<p>Leave Hyderabad by <strong>Telangana Express (12723)</strong> at <strong>06:00(AM) Hrs.</strong> for <strong>Delhi</strong>. Overnight journey in the train.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(263, 10, '2', 'New Delhi', 'New Delhi', '<p>Arrive <strong>New Delhi</strong> at <strong>07:40 hrs.</strong> Transfer to the hotel for wash and change. After breakfast, visit <strong>Lotus Temple</strong> followed by <strong>Akshardham Temple</strong>. Lunch at Akshardham Temple. Post lunch, visit <strong>India-Gate</strong>, <strong>Rashtrapati Bhavan, Kartavya Path</strong> <strong>(from outside)</strong>. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Delhi</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(264, 10, '3', 'New Delhi', 'Amritsar', '<p>After breakfast, leave <strong>Delhi</strong> for <strong>Amritsar</strong> by <strong>Shatabdi Express</strong> at <strong>07:20(AM) hrs</strong>. Arrive <strong>Amritsar</strong> at <strong>13:40 hrs. (01:40 PM)</strong>. Transfer to hotel. Post lunch leave for <strong>Wagah Border</strong> (the last Indian Check Post on the Indo-Pakistan border) to see change of guards and the flag hoisting and lowering activities done skillfully and with precision by the border security forces of both the countries. In the evening visit <strong>Durgiana Mandir</strong>. Return to hotel. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Amritsar</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(265, 10, '4', 'Amritsar', 'Dharamsala', '<p>After breakfast leave <strong>Amritsar</strong> for <strong>Dharamshala</strong>.&nbsp;Arrive <strong>Dharamshala</strong>, transfer to the hotel. After lunch visit <strong>Dalai Lamas Spiritual Center</strong>, <strong>Bakshunath Temple</strong> (to view the scenic beauty of the Himalian Hills).&nbsp;Dinner overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Dharamshala</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(266, 10, '5', 'Dharamsala', 'Dharamsala', '<p>After breakfast visit to <strong>Bhagsu Falls</strong>, <strong>Dal Lake</strong>, <strong>Tibetan Institute Of Performing Arts, Nechung Monastery</strong>. Day free for independent activities. &nbsp;Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Dharamshala</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(267, 10, '6', 'Dharamsala', 'New Delhi', '<p>After breakfast leave <strong>Dharamshala</strong> for <strong>Jalandhar</strong>. Lunch at Haveli Jalandhar. Leave <strong>Jalandhar</strong> by <strong>Shatabdi Exp (12030) </strong>at <strong>17:57 hrs.</strong>&nbsp;Arrive <strong>New Delhi</strong> at <strong>23:05 hrs.</strong>&nbsp;Overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Delhi</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(268, 10, '7', 'New Delhi', 'Hyderabad', '<p>After breakfast visit <strong>Qutub Minar</strong> (The Qutb Minar, also spelled Qutub Minar and Qutab Minar, is a minaret and \"victory tower\" that forms part of the Qutb complex, which lies at the site of Delhis oldest fortified city) and Airforce Museum. Post lunch transfer to <strong>New Delhi Railway Station</strong> to board <strong>Telangana Express (12724)</strong> for <strong>Hyderabad</strong> at <strong>17:30 hrs</strong>. Dinner and overnight journey in the train.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(269, 10, '8', 'Hyderabad', 'Hyderabad', '<p>Arrive <strong>Hyderabad </strong>at <strong>19:50 hrs (07:50 PM).</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:43:51', '2023-02-27 08:43:51'),
(282, 7, '1', 'Jaipur', 'New Delhi', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Leave <strong>Jaipur</strong> at <strong>22:00 Hrs. (10:00 PM)</strong> for <strong>Delhi</strong> by A/c Bus. Overnight journey in the A/c bus.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:57:44', '2023-02-27 08:57:44'),
(283, 7, '2', 'New Delhi', 'Kochi', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Arrive <strong>Delhi</strong>, and transfer to the <strong>Indira Gandhi International Airport</strong> to board flight for <strong>Kochi</strong>. Arrive <strong>Kochi</strong> and visit <strong>Jewish Synagogue, and Mattancherry Palace</strong> and return back to the hotel for lunch. After lunch enjoy the <strong>Cruise at</strong> <strong>Kochi Harbor and seven island.</strong> Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Kochi.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:57:44', '2023-02-27 08:57:44'),
(284, 7, '3', 'Kochi', 'Kochi', '<p>After breakfast visit the famous <strong>Wonderla</strong> the best amusement park of Kerala.&nbsp;Lunch at Wonderla. Evening free for shopping and independent activities.&nbsp;Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Kochi.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:57:44', '2023-02-27 08:57:44'),
(285, 7, '4', 'Kochi', 'Munnar', '<p>After breakfast, leave <strong>Kochi</strong> for <strong>Munnar.</strong> Arrive <strong>Munnar</strong> and transfer to the hotel for lunch. Post lunch, visit <strong style=\"color: black;\">Eravikulam National Park, Mattupetty Dam, Waterfalls &amp; Echo Point, Tea Plantations</strong>. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Munnar.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:57:44', '2023-02-27 08:57:44'),
(286, 7, '5', 'Munnar', 'Thekkady', '<p><span style=\"color: black;\">After breakfast, leave </span><strong style=\"color: black;\">Munnar</strong><span style=\"color: black;\"> for </span><strong style=\"color: black;\">Thekkady</strong><span style=\"color: black;\">. Arrive </span><strong style=\"color: black;\">Thekkedy</strong><span style=\"color: black;\"> </span>visit <strong>Periyar Lake, Green Park </strong>return back to hotel for lunch. Post lunch visit<strong> Ayurvedic &amp; Spices Plantation</strong><span style=\"color: black;\"> dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at </span><strong style=\"color: black;\">Thekkedy.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:57:44', '2023-02-27 08:57:44'),
(287, 7, '6', 'Thekkady', 'Kochi', '<p>After early breakfast leave for <strong>Alleppey </strong>(Lunch on the way).<strong> Arrive Alleppey</strong> and enjoy the <strong>back-water cruise.</strong> Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel <strong>at Kochi.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:57:44', '2023-02-27 08:57:44'),
(288, 7, '7', 'Kochi', 'Jaipur', '<p>Rise up early morning and transfer to the <strong>Cochin International Airport</strong> to board the flight for <strong>Delhi</strong>. Arrive <strong>Delhi</strong> and transfer to the A/c coach and leave for <strong>Jaipur</strong> (lunch on the way). Arrive <strong>Jaipur</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 08:57:44', '2023-02-27 08:57:44'),
(295, 8, '1', 'Hyderabad', 'New Delhi', '<p>Leave <strong>Hyderabad</strong> by <strong>Telangana Express (12723)</strong> at <strong>06:00(AM) Hrs.</strong> for <strong>Delhi</strong>. Lunch in the train. Dinner and overnight journey in the train.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:22:31', '2023-02-27 09:22:31'),
(296, 8, '2', 'New Delhi', 'Sawai Madhopur', '<p>Arrive <strong>New Delhi</strong> at <strong>07:40(AM) Hrs</strong>.<strong> </strong>Transfer to the hotel for wash and change. After breakfast, visit <strong>Prime Ministers Museum</strong>. Post lunch, leave for <strong>Sarai Rohilla Railway Station</strong>. En route visit, <strong>India Gate Rashtrapati Bhavan, Kartavya path (from outside)</strong>. Arrive Railway station and board<strong> Mewar Express (12963)</strong> at <strong>18:25 Hrs. (06:25 PM)</strong> for <strong>Sawai Madhopur</strong>. Arrive <strong>Sawai Madhopur</strong> at <strong>23:03 Hrs. (11:03 PM)</strong>. Check-in to the hotel. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Ranthambore</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:22:31', '2023-02-27 09:22:31'),
(297, 8, '3', 'Sawai Madhopur', 'Jaipur', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Early morning leave for <strong>Jeep Safari</strong> in <strong>Ranthambore National Park</strong> to spot wild animals like tiger, wild boar, cheetal, barking deer and various species of birds. Return to the hotel for breakfast. Visit <strong>Padam Talao</strong> and <strong>Ranthambore Fort</strong>. Post lunch, leave for <strong>Jaipur</strong>. Arrive <strong>Jaipur</strong>. Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Jaipur</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:22:31', '2023-02-27 09:22:31'),
(298, 8, '4', 'Jaipur', 'Jaipur', '<p>After breakfast, visit <strong>City Palace</strong> and <strong>Hawa Mahal</strong>. Post lunch visit <strong>Albert Hall Museum</strong> (the oldest museum of the state and functions as the state museum of Rajasthan. The building is situated in Ram Niwas garden outside the city wall opposite New gate and is a fine example of Indo-Saracenic architecture). Evening free for independent activities and shopping at <strong>Bapu Bazar</strong>. Dinner with dance party at the hotel. Overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Jaipur</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:22:31', '2023-02-27 09:22:31'),
(299, 8, '5', 'Jaipur', 'Jaipur', '<p>After breakfast, visit <strong>Amber Fort</strong> (Amer Fort is known for its artistic style elements. With its large ramparts and series of gates and cobbled paths, the fort overlooks Maota Lake, which is the main source of water for the Amer Palace). Post lunch transfer to the <strong>Railway Station</strong> to board <strong>Jaipur Hyderabad Express (12719)</strong> at <strong>15:30 Hrs. (03:30 PM)</strong> for <strong>Hyderabad.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:22:31', '2023-02-27 09:22:31'),
(300, 8, '6', 'Hyderabad', 'Hyderabad', '<p>Arrive <strong>Hyderabad</strong>.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:22:31', '2023-02-27 09:22:31'),
(307, 9, '1', 'Hyderabad', 'Bangaluru', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Leave <strong>Kachiguda </strong>by <strong style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">KCG MYS SF EXP</strong><strong> (</strong><strong style=\"color: black;\">12785)</strong><span style=\"color: black;\"> at </span><strong style=\"color: black;\">19:05 hrs.</strong><strong> (07:05 PM)</strong> for <strong>Bangalore. </strong>Overnight journey by train.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:59:27', '2023-02-27 09:59:27'),
(308, 9, '2', 'Bangaluru', 'Bangaluru', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Arrive <strong>Bangalore</strong> at <strong>06:40 Hrs (AM)</strong> and transfer to the hotel for wash and change. Post breakfast, visit <strong>Tipus Summer Palace </strong>(Tipu Sultan\'s Summer Palace, in Bangalore is an example of Indo-Islamic architecture and was the summer residence of the Mysorean ruler Tipu Sultan). Return to the Hotel for lunch. Post lunch, visit <strong>Visvesvaraya Science Museum </strong>(popularly known as Visvesvaraya Museum its a constituent unit of National Council of Science Museums (NCSM), Ministry of Culture, Government of India, was established in memory of Bharat Ratna Sir M. Visvesvaraya) and <strong>Vidhana Soudha</strong> (from outside)<strong>. </strong>In the evening, visit <strong>Bull Temple.</strong> Dinner and overnight stay in hotel at <strong>Bangalore.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:59:27', '2023-02-27 09:59:27'),
(309, 9, '3', 'Bangaluru', 'Madikeri', '<p>After breakfast, leave <strong>Bangalore </strong>for <strong>Coorg (Madikeri) </strong>by AC Bus. &nbsp;Arrive Coorg by lunchtime. Post lunch; visit<strong> Abbey Falls</strong> (a popular waterfall in Kodagu district. River Kaveri drops for about 70 ft over wide rocks creating a spectacular view) Evening free for independent activities. Dinner and overnight stay in the Hotel at <strong>Coorg (Madikeri).</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:59:27', '2023-02-27 09:59:27'),
(310, 9, '4', 'Madikeri', 'Mysore', '<p>After early breakfast, leave <strong>Coorg (Madikeri)</strong> for <strong>Mysore. </strong>Enroute visit <strong>Madikeri Fort </strong>(Madikeri Fort is one of the many forts built or rebuilt by Tipu Sultan during his reign in the second half of the 18th century).<strong> </strong>Arrive Mysore and transfer to the hotel. Post lunch, visit <strong>Mysore Palace</strong> (Mysore Palace, also known as Amba Vilas Palace and Mysore Aramane, is one of the most magnificent and largest palaces in India) and leave for<strong> Brindavan Gardens.</strong> Dinner and overnight stay in the hotel at <strong>Mysore.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:59:27', '2023-02-27 09:59:27'),
(311, 9, '5', 'Mysore', 'Bangaluru', '<p>After breakfast; check out from the hotel and leave <strong>Mysore</strong> for <strong>Bangalore</strong>. On the way, visit <strong>Hindustan Aeronautics Limited (HAL) Museum. </strong>Arrive<strong> </strong>Bangalore<strong>. </strong>Post lunch, day free for independent activities.<strong> </strong>In the evening, transfer to the railway station to board the <strong>Bangalore Kachiguda Express (12786)</strong> at <strong>18:20</strong> for <strong>Hyderabad (Kachiguda)</strong>. Overnight journey in the train.</p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:59:27', '2023-02-27 09:59:27'),
(312, 9, '6', 'Hyderabad', 'Hyderabad', '<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Arrive <strong>Hyderabad</strong> at <strong>05:40 Hrs.</strong></p>', '1', '2023-02-27 09:59:27', '2023-02-27 09:59:27');
